03:14.350 --> 03:14.910
goes to

03:14.910 --> 03:16.620
our new classmate

03:16.650 --> 03:17.790
Zhu Panpan again.

03:17.790 --> 03:19.329
Let's give him a big hand.

03:23.910 --> 03:24.910
Do you like

03:24.930 --> 03:26.000
your new classmate?

03:26.140 --> 03:27.990
Yes!

03:28.100 --> 03:28.829
But,

03:28.850 --> 03:29.780
since Zhu Panpan

03:29.810 --> 03:31.510
is new in our class,

03:31.510 --> 03:33.100
he is still unfamiliar with everyone,

03:33.350 --> 03:33.990
so

03:34.020 --> 03:35.620
he seldom speaks.

03:35.860 --> 03:37.450
Can we give him a hand?

03:38.230 --> 03:40.060
How about we

03:40.190 --> 03:41.340
take the initiative to make friends with him

03:41.370 --> 03:41.950
and encourage him to speak more?

03:42.350 --> 03:44.020
Sure!

03:47.740 --> 03:48.490
Hello,

03:48.740 --> 03:51.100
if you make friends with me,

03:51.270 --> 03:53.940
these snacks are all yours.

03:54.180 --> 03:55.400
They are yummy.

03:55.930 --> 03:58.380
They are yummy.

04:01.270 --> 04:02.250
I'm Wang Lunye.

04:03.650 --> 04:04.920
If you make friends with me,

04:05.540 --> 04:07.940
this is yours,

04:08.560 --> 04:10.470
and I can have the chauffeur

04:10.470 --> 04:11.340
pick you up to my place.

04:11.890 --> 04:13.890
