04:54.050 --> 04:55.810
He can keep silent if he wants.

05:16.520 --> 05:17.170
Thank you.

05:17.700 --> 05:18.910
What's your name?

05:20.960 --> 05:22.020
My name is Su Chengcheng.

05:27.830 --> 05:29.200
