05:29.480 --> 05:31.380
♫You are my sunshine♫

05:31.760 --> 05:34.020
♫My only sunshine♫

05:34.460 --> 05:37.000
♫You make me happy♫

05:37.020 --> 05:38.590
♫When skies are grey♫

05:39.540 --> 05:44.340
♫You never know dear how much I love you♫

05:45.050 --> 05:49.120
♫Please don't take my sunshine away♫

06:07.270 --> 06:07.630
Zhu…

06:10.440 --> 06:10.980
Zhu Panpan?

06:13.820 --> 06:14.510
Keep dancing.

06:14.830 --> 06:15.420
Zhu Panpan!

06:15.840 --> 06:16.920
Come on, keep dancing!

06:35.590 --> 06:36.670
Zhu Panpan

06:36.670 --> 06:37.450
is outstanding in many ways,

06:37.770 --> 06:39.250
and he was first again in the last exam.

06:40.070 --> 06:41.870
It's just his personality.

06:42.370 --> 06:43.740
He is too shy and timid.

06:44.590 --> 06:45.130
It's such…

06:45.470 --> 06:46.550
