06:46.550 --> 06:47.440
What's the big deal?

06:49.220 --> 06:50.530
I don't care if the room gets

06:50.770 --> 06:51.630
dirty or untidy.

06:52.030 --> 06:52.870
Just stamp on these balloons

06:52.870 --> 06:53.740
till all of them are burst.

06:54.590 --> 06:54.990
Come on,

06:55.310 --> 06:55.860
