07:13.010 --> 07:13.590
Watch!

07:18.290 --> 07:18.840
You see.

07:19.160 --> 07:19.650
See.

07:21.750 --> 07:22.230
See.

07:22.310 --> 07:22.870
Mom.

07:23.870 --> 07:24.550
Mom.

07:24.750 --> 07:25.280
See.

07:25.310 --> 07:25.750
See.

07:26.150 --> 07:26.490
Come on.

07:27.260 --> 07:27.620
Come on.

07:27.990 --> 07:28.440
Stamp!

07:29.350 --> 07:29.810
Stamp!

07:30.400 --> 07:31.270
Just stamp!

07:31.970 --> 07:32.390
Stamp!

