08:26.910 --> 08:29.230
But I only got 74 .

08:38.549 --> 08:39.350
Don't be afraid.

08:39.669 --> 08:41.110
I'll walk you home.

08:45.060 --> 08:45.740
Here you go.

08:46.380 --> 08:47.980
Refreshing pickled cucumber.

08:50.460 --> 08:51.130
Enjoy yourselves!

08:54.790 --> 08:56.210
Auntie, it's so yummy.

08:56.230 --> 08:57.610
Can I have another bowl of rice?

08:58.340 --> 08:58.860
Yes.

08:59.060 --> 08:59.430
Of course.

09:05.100 --> 09:05.480
Would you like some more?

09:06.390 --> 09:06.880
No more, thanks.

09:10.990 --> 09:11.710
Auntie.

09:11.920 --> 09:12.670
If my mom can

09:12.710 --> 09:13.710
cook such delicious food,

09:13.710 --> 09:15.320
