09:16.850 --> 09:18.130
Enjoy yourself if you like it.

09:18.660 --> 09:19.580
Eat this.

09:23.320 --> 09:23.880
Mom,

09:24.840 --> 09:25.930
I'd like another bowl, too.

09:29.470 --> 09:29.920
OK,

09:31.100 --> 09:31.880
give me the bowl.

09:37.180 --> 09:39.410
Auntie, Zhu Panpan is so smart!

09:39.950 --> 09:41.030
