09:43.470 --> 09:44.310
but he's the only one that

09:44.310 --> 09:45.590
got a 90 plus.

09:45.820 --> 09:46.520
Really?

09:47.270 --> 09:48.070
His score is about a dozen points higher

09:48.090 --> 09:49.620
than the second place.

09:49.790 --> 09:51.190
Our teacher always tells us

09:51.190 --> 09:52.240
to follow his example.

09:52.590 --> 09:54.110
Auntie, you are such a good mother

09:54.110 --> 09:55.910
that you've educated Zhu Panpan to be so outstanding.

09:56.220 --> 09:57.380
And you cook such delicious food.

09:57.640 --> 09:58.680
Are you a fairy?

10:01.870 --> 10:03.160
You are the little fairy.

10:03.630 --> 10:04.720
If you like the food,

10:04.740 --> 10:06.100
come and enjoy it anytime you want.

10:07.650 --> 10:09.100
I've never seen Panpan

10:09.470 --> 10:10.430
have the second bowl of rice before.

10:12.070 --> 10:13.250
Because of you,

10:13.810 --> 10:14.640
