10:16.030 --> 10:17.150
Here.

10:17.150 --> 10:17.520
Have some meat.

10:20.130 --> 10:21.020
Want some more, Panpan?

10:22.410 --> 10:23.190
Eat this.

10:23.900 --> 10:24.360
Thanks.

10:41.750 --> 10:42.990
Don't play with Zhu Panpan.

10:43.060 --> 10:43.700
Yes, I agree.

10:43.790 --> 10:44.590
He's so strange.

10:44.920 --> 10:45.820
No wonder he has no friends.

10:56.370 --> 10:58.000
Zhu Panpan, would you like my popsicle?

10:58.700 --> 10:59.960
One half for you and another half for me.

11:01.180 --> 11:02.090
What's the next line?

11:02.630 --> 11:03.030
Oh, right.

11:03.190 --> 11:04.400
One half for you and another half for me.

11:04.710 --> 11:05.590
You are my best friend

11:05.590 --> 11:06.880
forever.

11:07.270 --> 11:08.250
Let's go to the same senior high school

11:08.290 --> 11:09.690
and college in the future,

11:09.880 --> 11:11.390
so that we'll be together forever.

11:20.260 --> 11:21.460
Thank you, Su Chengcheng.

11:23.450 --> 11:24.830
Take the most valued thing of mine

11:24.830 --> 11:25.420
as a gift.

11:26.730 --> 11:28.750
Then you are my best friend

11:28.750 --> 11:29.560
forever, too.

11:40.340 --> 11:40.960
Cheers.

11:57.820 --> 11:58.770
