12:38.350 --> 12:39.110
I like you.

12:40.000 --> 12:40.320
No,

12:40.920 --> 12:41.880
you don't like me at all.

12:43.910 --> 12:44.690
- I mean…
- Don't move.

12:45.710 --> 12:46.440
