12:48.550 --> 12:49.590
How do you want me to prove that

12:49.590 --> 12:50.150
I like you?

12:50.630 --> 12:51.830
Now that you've joined our lab

12:51.830 --> 12:53.100
and become a member of our research group,

12:53.190 --> 12:54.470
we should use scientific methods

12:54.470 --> 12:54.920
to prove it.

12:55.260 --> 12:55.760
Like, do experiments.

12:57.000 --> 12:57.650
Do experiments

12:58.540 --> 12:59.670
to prove I like you?

13:00.030 --> 13:00.330
Yes.

13:03.380 --> 13:03.950
Ms. Chen.

13:05.340 --> 13:06.860
That's a valuable discussion.

13:07.750 --> 13:09.310
The research topic of emotion brain-computer interface

13:09.310 --> 13:10.490
is also about that.

13:12.120 --> 13:12.740
How about

13:13.350 --> 13:14.620
you

13:14.290 --> 13:18.940
[Head of Southeast Sci-Tech University Brain and Intelligence Lab]

13:14.290 --> 13:18.940
[Chen Yourong]

13:14.870 --> 13:15.980
design a simple experiment

13:16.590 --> 13:17.830
to see

13:17.830 --> 13:18.390
whether it's possible to

13:18.390 --> 13:19.630
tell whether one is into another

13:19.630 --> 13:20.670
through external indications?

13:21.650 --> 13:23.310
Let's make it the theme

13:23.360 --> 13:24.580
of our next sharing session.

13:27.830 --> 13:28.830
I've always believed that

13:28.870 --> 13:30.460
there are only two results of a declaration of love.

13:30.910 --> 13:32.300
Yes or no.

13:32.900 --> 13:34.550
I didn't see the third one coming:

13:35.110 --> 13:35.950
do experiments.

13:37.230 --> 13:38.350
But before the so-called

13:38.350 --> 13:39.740
love experiment,

13:40.160 --> 13:41.240
I have to…

13:43.290 --> 13:43.930
Chengcheng,

13:44.350 --> 13:45.470
your task for today

13:45.470 --> 13:46.880
is to clean the lab.

13:55.350 --> 13:56.770
It's so messy.

13:57.470 --> 13:58.200
Don't say that,

13:58.670 --> 13:59.640
Chengcheng.

14:00.530 --> 14:01.220
Do you have any idea

14:01.250 --> 14:02.910
how many valuable achievements

14:02.940 --> 14:04.700
are born from the mess?

14:04.860 --> 14:06.180
You only see the mess

14:06.630 --> 14:07.110
without noticing

14:07.110 --> 14:09.460
the serious meaning behind it.

14:10.800 --> 14:12.040
Yes, of course.

14:14.760 --> 14:15.610
Oh right, Chengcheng.

14:16.390 --> 14:17.520
It is imperative

14:17.550 --> 14:18.710
to put on the lab-gown

14:18.780 --> 14:19.620
before entering the lab.

14:20.390 --> 14:20.770
OK.

15:01.050 --> 15:03.040
I almost forgot these.

15:19.780 --> 15:20.480
Chengcheng,

15:21.630 --> 15:22.230
it's cleaned

15:22.230 --> 15:23.110
all by yourself?

15:24.700 --> 15:25.250
Is it up to standard?

15:26.070 --> 15:26.770
Yes, of course.

15:28.850 --> 15:30.590
It's beyond the standard.

15:30.590 --> 15:30.950
Good job.

15:38.900 --> 15:39.540
It…

15:41.260 --> 15:42.220
Is also cleaned by me.

15:42.430 --> 15:43.070
Neat, isn't it?

15:43.180 --> 15:43.490
What?

15:43.510 --> 15:44.200
Well,

15:44.430 --> 15:45.110
have you seen

15:45.130 --> 15:46.090
