15:46.260 --> 15:46.810
Oh, those.

15:46.840 --> 15:47.380
They were thrown away.

15:47.470 --> 15:48.390
Thrown away?

15:48.730 --> 15:49.330
What?

15:49.350 --> 15:50.310
They've gone bad.

15:50.390 --> 15:51.710
They were used to practice suturing

15:51.710 --> 15:52.710
by our senior,

15:52.730 --> 15:53.360
and now you threw them away.

15:53.730 --> 15:54.530
If she asks,

15:54.560 --> 15:55.390
do not mention me.

15:55.720 --> 15:56.590
I've never been here.

15:58.110 --> 15:58.660
Jiafa.

15:58.940 --> 15:59.710
Chengcheng.

16:00.140 --> 16:00.930
Good luck.

16:07.590 --> 16:09.060
Is she so terrifying?

16:10.990 --> 16:12.150
I'm screwed.

16:35.420 --> 16:36.250
These two

16:37.150 --> 16:38.030
should do.

16:41.220 --> 16:42.160
There you go.

