You want to use my phone, huh?

17:57.910 --> 17:58.510
Where's my phone?

17:58.510 --> 17:59.270
Give it back.

17:59.700 --> 18:01.140
Where's it?

18:01.670 --> 18:02.550
Tell me!

18:02.550 --> 18:03.470
Where's it?

18:03.610 --> 18:05.140
Come on,

18:05.170 --> 18:06.050
