18:07.850 --> 18:09.150
Clumsy as you, you think

18:09.310 --> 18:10.150
you can get out of this?

18:10.150 --> 18:11.110
How dare you.

18:11.110 --> 18:11.710
Where's my phone?

18:11.710 --> 18:12.720
Tell me!

18:15.060 --> 18:15.860
Where is it?

18:15.890 --> 18:16.860
There are only several pockets.

18:19.350 --> 18:20.070
Here it is.

18:20.200 --> 18:20.860
Thanks.

18:21.380 --> 18:22.570
Use your head.

18:26.540 --> 18:27.130
Don't move.

18:27.460 --> 18:28.020
He's yours.

18:28.040 --> 18:28.330
OK,

18:28.360 --> 18:29.090
we'll have him.

18:29.120 --> 18:29.500
Thanks for your help.

18:30.190 --> 18:30.590
Chengcheng.

18:30.820 --> 18:31.790
- Get up.
- Did you get your things back?

18:31.990 --> 18:32.630
Yes.

18:32.790 --> 18:33.510
They are brought by you?

18:33.540 --> 18:34.080
Thank you.

18:34.110 --> 18:35.130
It's not a big deal.

18:36.880 --> 18:37.930
Thank you!

18:39.190 --> 18:40.060
Goodbye!

18:41.740 --> 18:43.310
She's so cool,

18:45.690 --> 18:46.210
isn't she?

18:48.830 --> 18:50.380
He's Gu Chen, our monitor.

18:50.670 --> 18:51.810
He's very nice,

18:52.140 --> 18:54.690
always with a mysterious smile.

19:15.990 --> 19:18.300
Zhu Jiafa,

19:20.610 --> 19:21.870
where are my oranges?

19:25.990 --> 19:26.670
It's her?

19:32.070 --> 19:32.920
Senior Xixi.

19:32.950 --> 19:34.310
What a coincidence!

19:34.310 --> 19:34.880
Oranges?

19:35.160 --> 19:35.670
What oranges?

19:36.240 --> 19:36.980
Those two you use to

19:37.070 --> 19:38.770
