20:39.990 --> 20:41.030
see her again.

20:42.110 --> 20:42.580
Oh no,

20:43.030 --> 20:44.110
please don't tell me she's a member

20:44.180 --> 20:45.330
of tomorrow's love experiment.

20:46.920 --> 20:47.460
Su Chengcheng.

20:48.460 --> 20:49.270
Are you ready?

20:50.480 --> 20:51.310
Yes.

21:43.120 --> 21:44.380
Obvious change in heart rate.

21:50.740 --> 21:52.470
0.5℃ higher in body temperature.

22:05.020 --> 22:08.510
[1st Love experiment]

22:05.020 --> 22:08.510
