Higher body temperature,

22:41.300 --> 22:42.140
dilated pupils,

22:42.140 --> 22:42.910
increased heart rate,

22:42.930 --> 22:44.010
and faster blood flow.

22:44.540 --> 22:45.110
Aren't all of these

22:45.140 --> 22:46.060
the demonstrations of a crush?

22:46.270 --> 22:47.550
You still don't believe I like you?

22:47.670 --> 22:49.040
There's something wrong with the experiment design.

22:49.720 --> 22:51.050
