22:51.070 --> 22:52.020
don't have to be the signs

22:52.060 --> 22:53.140
of a crush.

22:53.820 --> 22:54.600
They can also be resulted from

22:55.060 --> 22:56.260
external stimuli.

22:56.700 --> 22:58.070
