You can't

23:36.070 --> 23:36.990
jump to the conclusion

23:37.270 --> 23:37.910
just based on

23:37.940 --> 23:39.090
the changes in my data

23:39.120 --> 23:40.190
just now.

23:42.740 --> 23:43.870
Under the same condition,

23:43.870 --> 23:45.590
the changes in the data.

23:45.590 --> 23:46.400
of your body temperature,

23:46.480 --> 23:48.130
pupil size,

23:48.170 --> 23:49.250
heart rate and blood flow

23:49.270 --> 23:49.950
are much greater

23:49.980 --> 23:51.020
when you were facing Senior Xixi.

23:52.830 --> 23:53.280
What?

23:54.010 --> 23:55.100
You like Zhang Xixi?

24:00.710 --> 24:01.260
Xiao Yuhe.

24:02.880 --> 24:04.160
Is the experiment

24:04.520 --> 24:05.560
only your excuse

24:05.950 --> 24:07.030
to

24:07.030 --> 24:08.120
reject me?

24:08.240 --> 24:10.250
