24:11.430 --> 24:12.380
How can I respond?

24:15.200 --> 24:16.430
I will prove it to you.

24:26.050 --> 24:27.710
I want ten ox tendons,

24:27.710 --> 24:28.470
ten bull backstraps,

24:28.470 --> 24:29.710
ten lamb kebabs,

24:29.710 --> 24:30.770
five squids,

24:30.800 --> 24:31.660
five gristles,

24:31.680 --> 24:32.900
two bean curd rolls…

24:32.950 --> 24:33.550
Wait a minute,

24:33.710 --> 24:34.640
how are you going to finish them all?

24:34.900 --> 24:35.940
Even a pig can't.

24:38.710 --> 24:39.770
Don't worry.

24:39.940 --> 24:40.650
I've got you.

24:41.100 --> 24:42.020
And two chicken wings.

24:47.390 --> 24:49.850
50, 51, 52.

24:50.790 --> 24:51.250
Come on.

24:51.550 --> 24:53.060
You have eaten

24:53.060 --> 24:53.590
too much.

24:53.590 --> 24:54.380
Stop eating.

24:55.440 --> 24:55.910
No,

24:57.180 --> 24:57.930
I feel sad.

24:58.730 --> 25:00.140
I need to produce dopamine by eating

25:00.210 --> 25:01.060
