25:09.030 --> 25:09.940
I wouldn't believe it if I were him.

25:10.420 --> 25:11.230
How can I not know

25:11.230 --> 25:12.330
who I like?

25:12.620 --> 25:13.590
- You don't know.
- I do know.

25:19.520 --> 25:20.560
Listen, Li Meizi,

25:21.050 --> 25:22.720
I'm going back to the dorm.

25:22.750 --> 25:23.670
I'll stay up studying,

25:23.670 --> 25:24.560
and find out the evidence

25:24.580 --> 25:25.800
to prove Xiao Yuhe's refutation

25:25.840 --> 25:27.450
is also wrong.

25:27.590 --> 25:28.260
I'm going.

25:31.480 --> 25:32.030
The barbecue!

25:58.190 --> 25:58.760
Hello,

25:59.140 --> 25:59.990
I'm Musk.

26:00.030 --> 26:00.770
Yes!

26:01.860 --> 26:02.400
Yes!

26:04.030 --> 26:05.140
Start scanning.

26:05.610 --> 26:06.430
Xiao Yuhe,

26:06.460 --> 26:13.770
[Musk  Developed by: Xiao Yuhe]

26:06.460 --> 26:13.770
[Type: Companion robot]

26:06.460 --> 26:13.770
[Phase: With expression recognition function]

26:06.790 --> 26:09.240
your current emotion is running high.

26:09.510 --> 26:10.070
You are excited.

26:33.230 --> 26:34.490
Who didn't lock the door?

26:56.260 --> 26:57.060
Some say

26:57.650 --> 26:59.880
love is a well-matched game,

27:00.830 --> 27:01.350
but in this uneven-matched game

27:01.350 --> 27:02.790
of mine,

27:03.120 --> 27:04.050
I will die

27:04.750 --> 27:07.120
for love.

27:13.190 --> 27:13.840
Good morning, Jiafa.

27:14.390 --> 27:14.970
Chengcheng,

27:17.110 --> 27:18.490
didn't I tell you

27:18.920 --> 27:20.550
not to have food or drinks in the office?

27:37.790 --> 27:38.710
I'm sorry, Jiafa.

27:38.740 --> 27:39.470
I'll have it outside.

27:40.120 --> 27:40.870
Wait.

27:42.400 --> 27:43.270
Why are you using a spoon

27:43.310 --> 27:44.310
instead of a straw

27:44.390 --> 27:45.010
to drink bubble tea?

27:46.320 --> 27:47.610
There are plenty of toppings in it.

27:48.060 --> 27:49.340
Like crushed peanuts,

27:49.590 --> 27:50.500
raisins,

27:50.530 --> 27:52.070
coconut jelly, pudding,

27:52.070 --> 27:52.870
and some other toppings.

27:52.870 --> 27:54.200
I can't suck them in with a straw.

27:54.460 --> 27:56.210
And it's called bubble tea?

27:56.230 --> 27:57.570
Why not grass jelly?

27:57.720 --> 27:59.440
They are different.

27:59.850 --> 28:01.330
The bubble tea tastes more delicious this way.

28:07.770 --> 28:09.070
I bought one and got one free.

28:09.630 --> 28:10.450
Would you like to try?

28:13.120 --> 28:13.520
No, no,

28:14.590 --> 28:14.920
thanks.

28:20.030 --> 28:20.550
See?

28:20.550 --> 28:21.510
I can suck them in.

28:21.810 --> 28:22.870
You're good.

28:23.190 --> 28:24.390
If you like it,

28:24.390 --> 28:25.310
I can always bring you one cup

28:25.310 --> 28:25.870
when I buy it.

28:25.870 --> 28:26.900
She's nice.

28:29.300 --> 28:30.040
These days,

28:31.140 --> 28:32.230
you don't understand.

28:32.970 --> 28:34.570
I didn't mean to…

28:50.670 --> 28:51.230
Prof. Du.

29:00.350 --> 29:00.940
Xiao Yuhe,

29:01.830 --> 29:02.510
I did a lot of research

29:02.510 --> 29:03.620
last night.

29:04.070 --> 29:05.110
To tell

29:05.110 --> 29:06.030
whether one is into another

29:06.030 --> 29:07.160
through physiological data

29:07.190 --> 29:08.100
is a one-way experiment.

29:08.470 --> 29:09.990
When you are into someone,

29:09.990 --> 29:10.990
your heart beats faster,

29:10.990 --> 29:12.350
you have a higher blood oxygen level,

29:12.350 --> 29:13.670
and produce more hormones.

29:13.670 --> 29:15.190
But we can't jump to the conclusion

29:15.190 --> 29:16.550
that one is into another

29:16.550 --> 29:17.990
based on

29:17.990 --> 29:19.230
these simple changes.

29:19.590 --> 29:20.000
So

29:20.030 --> 29:21.220
even if

29:21.220 --> 29:22.350
all my experimental data

29:22.350 --> 29:23.000
meet the requirements,

29:23.370 --> 29:24.660
I still can't prove I'm into you.

29:25.440 --> 29:26.600
You are making me prove

29:26.630 --> 29:27.670
something that cannot be proved.

29:29.710 --> 29:30.960
Seems you really did a lot of research.

29:31.270 --> 29:31.990
It is impossible to prove

29:31.990 --> 29:32.980
whether one is into another.

29:34.800 --> 29:35.510
What do you mean?

29:35.660 --> 29:36.470
You are in favor of me?

29:36.770 --> 29:38.280
We can't prove whether one is into another,

29:37.370 --> 29:39.420
[Brain and Intelligence Lab]

29:37.370 --> 29:39.420
[Likes proving experiments]

29:38.590 --> 29:39.630
but we can observe it.

29:39.750 --> 29:41.070
In 2003,

29:41.070 --> 29:41.910
Helen Fisher and her lab members

29:41.910 --> 29:43.270
scanned the brains of 17 couples

29:43.270 --> 29:44.420
through MRI

29:44.470 --> 29:45.070
and found apparent activation

29:45.070 --> 29:46.470
in the ventral tegmentum and caudate nucleus

29:46.510 --> 29:47.390
of the midbrain

29:47.420 --> 29:48.540
when they looked at

29:48.570 --> 29:49.720
the photos of their partners.

29:49.750 --> 29:51.110
And the more they love each other,

29:51.110 --> 29:52.350
the more active

29:52.350 --> 29:52.940
the two areas are.

29:53.070 --> 29:54.150
So through observation on

29:54.150 --> 29:55.550
the two areas

29:55.630 --> 29:56.620
we can tell whether

29:56.820 --> 29:57.950
one is into the other.

29:58.520 --> 29:59.630
We need to redo the experiment.

30:00.230 --> 30:01.120
Again?

30:02.310 --> 30:03.390
When we were

30:03.390 --> 30:04.630
doing the NIR brain function imaging,

30:04.630 --> 30:05.950
the ventral tegmentum

30:05.950 --> 30:07.270
and caudate nucleus of your midbrain were not activated.

30:07.330 --> 30:07.970
You explained

30:07.990 --> 30:09.110
it was due to the ambience in the lab,

30:09.150 --> 30:09.750
so we can cultivate the ambience

30:09.750 --> 30:10.630
between us before

30:10.630 --> 30:12.030
the next data collection.

30:12.950 --> 30:13.910
What do you mean?

30:14.020 --> 30:14.860
I mean going on a date,

30:15.110 --> 30:16.110
doing something

30:16.110 --> 30:16.860
common for couples

30:16.890 --> 30:18.290
to get us closer

30:18.380 --> 30:19.150
so that

30:19.150 --> 30:19.950
the relative functional areas

30:19.950 --> 30:20.950
in your brain

30:20.950 --> 30:22.150
will be fully activated

30:22.150 --> 30:23.350
when doing the NIR imaging.

30:29.580 --> 30:30.460
A date…

30:48.270 --> 30:49.030
You can decide

30:49.590 --> 30:50.710
the places you want to go

30:51.730 --> 30:52.580
and the things you want to do.

30:53.700 --> 30:54.410
Just let me know when you have decided.

30:55.360 --> 30:55.810
OK.

31:37.680 --> 31:38.490
My friends,

31:39.430 --> 31:40.900
he asked me out.

31:41.170 --> 31:42.300
On his own initiative.

31:55.800 --> 31:56.650
Have you decided where to go?

31:57.780 --> 31:58.670
I did some research.

31:58.670 --> 32:00.010
Red Brick Art Museum will do.

32:00.180 --> 32:01.660
There will be

32:01.690 --> 32:02.480
an installation art exhibition recently.

32:02.710 --> 32:04.430
It'll be nice

32:04.430 --> 32:05.630
to sit

32:05.630 --> 32:06.150
in the coffee shop nearby

32:06.220 --> 32:09.110
after seeing the exhibition.

32:09.710 --> 32:10.620
You are good.

32:10.640 --> 32:11.830
You really did a lot of research.

32:11.860 --> 32:13.460
That hurts.

32:14.400 --> 32:14.820
Chengcheng.

32:14.930 --> 32:15.330
Meizi.

32:15.670 --> 32:16.060
Monitor.

32:17.010 --> 32:18.330
The assignment of physics should be handed in tomorrow.

32:18.510 --> 32:19.800
And the time for the English test is also fixed.

32:20.110 --> 32:21.710
Only you two didn't reply in the class group.

32:21.920 --> 32:22.970
Oh God, stop, don't mention it.

32:23.840 --> 32:25.230
Didn't we just finish the internship

32:25.230 --> 32:26.310
of Electronic Technology

32:26.310 --> 32:27.450
