32:31.430 --> 32:33.000
I feel like I'm in Grade 12.

32:34.200 --> 32:35.180
I can't believe that.

32:35.510 --> 32:36.270
We are

32:36.270 --> 32:37.630
paying the tuition for one person,

32:37.630 --> 32:38.800
having a curriculum for two people,

32:38.820 --> 32:40.170
and doing assignments for four people.

32:40.390 --> 32:42.040
One minute there are assignments and exams,

32:42.070 --> 32:43.420
and the next there are experiments in the lab.

32:43.930 --> 32:44.890
I'm exhausted.

32:46.070 --> 32:46.740
But speaking of the lab,

32:46.950 --> 32:48.080
Chengcheng,

32:48.110 --> 32:49.150
the Brain and Intelligence Lab you picked

32:49.150 --> 32:49.800
is a national key subject.

32:50.410 --> 32:51.180
It's a good opportunity.

32:51.750 --> 32:52.790
Come on.

32:53.140 --> 32:55.220
All the members in my team are talented

32:55.530 --> 32:56.680
except me.

32:58.060 --> 32:59.050
Tell you what,

32:59.270 --> 33:00.070
there's a horrible senior

33:00.070 --> 33:01.640
in our lab...

33:05.870 --> 33:07.270
How come such a pretty face like you

33:07.390 --> 33:08.700
is so brazen?

33:09.510 --> 33:10.470
You will be over any boy you like,

33:10.470 --> 33:11.620
won't you?

33:11.850 --> 33:13.160
Who do you think you are to pursue Wang Jiaze?

33:15.220 --> 33:15.930
How dare she?

33:31.870 --> 33:32.630
Stop being mad.

33:34.090 --> 33:35.020
Calm yourself down.

33:53.510 --> 33:54.310
Will she think it was me

33:54.310 --> 33:55.160
who gave the cup to her?

33:57.860 --> 33:59.090
What should I do?

34:00.970 --> 34:01.800
What should I do?

34:04.030 --> 34:04.520
Chengcheng.

34:07.770 --> 34:08.460
Give it to her.

34:08.750 --> 34:09.630
- I don't dare.
- Talk to her.

34:09.870 --> 34:10.449
Talk to her.

34:10.610 --> 34:11.540
Just go!

34:26.449 --> 34:27.040
Senior.

34:27.440 --> 34:27.920
Um…

34:27.949 --> 34:29.239
- There's some tissue.
- Don't follow me.

34:39.630 --> 34:40.389
Jiafa.

34:43.510 --> 34:44.380
OK, I'm on my way.

34:50.980 --> 34:52.300
I just heard that

34:53.250 --> 34:54.460
you joined our lab

34:55.199 --> 34:55.980
all for

34:56.120 --> 34:58.110
dating Xiao Yuhe.

35:01.130 --> 35:02.240
I don't understand.

35:02.650 --> 35:04.240
Do you think this lab

35:04.270 --> 35:05.540
is suitable for you to date someone

35:06.190 --> 35:06.830
or

35:06.830 --> 35:08.190
you feel like dating someone

35:08.340 --> 35:09.680
once you enter the lab?

35:18.650 --> 35:20.050
Why don't you speak?

35:20.860 --> 35:22.360
You think I'm giving you a hard time?

35:24.430 --> 35:26.980
Do not distract him.

35:27.380 --> 35:28.260
Do you know

35:29.190 --> 35:30.390
how much hope we have placed

35:30.390 --> 35:31.780
on Xiao Yuhe?

35:32.190 --> 35:33.080
Do you know

35:33.100 --> 35:34.010
how precious

35:34.050 --> 35:35.170
his time for experiment is?

35:36.300 --> 35:37.440
Stop doing that.

35:48.860 --> 35:49.780
Is there anything else?

35:50.950 --> 35:51.510
You can go then.

35:53.370 --> 35:54.170
Goodbye, sir.

36:03.990 --> 36:04.530
Su Chengcheng,

36:09.090 --> 36:10.110
