36:16.390 --> 36:17.350
I'll let you know when I have decided.

36:43.150 --> 36:44.380
No wonder he's

36:44.580 --> 36:45.550
a curve wrecker.

36:46.270 --> 36:47.760
Cultivating ambience

36:48.030 --> 36:49.200
to get closer,

36:49.820 --> 36:52.170
monitoring the physiological data and brain movements.

36:52.990 --> 36:54.110
Just admit you are into her.

36:54.110 --> 36:55.080
Why does it have to be so roundabout?

36:55.170 --> 36:55.670
Right?

36:56.070 --> 36:57.060
Into me?

36:58.750 --> 36:59.660
Are you sure?

37:00.930 --> 37:01.670
It's natural for a man

37:01.710 --> 37:02.560
to be indirect

37:03.110 --> 37:03.830
in his confession

37:03.830 --> 37:04.890
of love.

37:06.100 --> 37:06.520
Chengcheng.

37:06.640 --> 37:07.440
Have you decided

37:07.470 --> 37:07.970
where you are going on a date?

37:09.510 --> 37:10.410
No, I haven't.

37:15.910 --> 37:16.390
Bro Ying,

37:16.510 --> 37:17.400
where are you going?

37:18.550 --> 37:20.030
The course Prof. Du teaches is a little difficult.

37:20.030 --> 37:20.590
I've borrowed

37:20.590 --> 37:21.710
the notes of a senior

37:21.710 --> 37:22.850
