37:23.150 --> 37:24.110
I'll go with you.

37:24.140 --> 37:25.390
I plan to preview, too.

37:25.450 --> 37:26.560
Can I borrow the notes?

37:27.110 --> 37:27.520
Sure.

37:39.150 --> 37:40.660
How diligent.

37:41.460 --> 37:42.990
It's so late and they still work hard.

37:51.870 --> 37:53.030
Where were we?

37:53.030 --> 37:54.170
Your date.

37:54.360 --> 37:55.680
Ask him!

37:55.710 --> 37:57.110
You need to know where is the date

37:57.110 --> 37:58.200
