Zhu Panpan!

38:52.510 --> 38:53.200
Zhu Panpan!

38:53.400 --> 38:54.330
I'm here.

38:54.970 --> 38:55.680
Come.

38:56.590 --> 38:57.460
Come here.

38:59.740 --> 39:00.510
Zhu Panpan,

39:00.700 --> 39:01.770
I'm here!

